		<title>12       NEW BRIGHTON</title>
		<content>  Basically this is a village for older
 people with very few facilities for   
 the young.The play area was           
 vandalised. There is an old tavern,   
 The Rose and Crown, and a new motel,  
 The Arches.There is a sweet shop and a
 grocery cum Post Office which is quite
 busy.There is a residential policeman 
 at the police station.New Brighton    
 having no schools,pupils attend Mynydd
 Isa Juniors or{Argoed High School}.   
 There is a chapel and a church, both  
 poorly attended other than at special 
 services.                             
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
